<div class="tc-v4-wrapper" id="tc-viz-4">
  <div class="tc-v4-box">
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 8px;">The Single-Entry Constraint</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">How long is a US B1/B2 visa actually valid? For the vast majority of African nations, it&#8217;s just 3 months and a single trip. Search or filter below to see the disparities.</p>
    
    <input type="text" id="tc-v4-search" class="tc-v4-input" placeholder="Search for a country..." onkeyup="tcFilterCards()">

    <div class="tc-v4-summary">
      <div class="tc-v4-badge tc-v4-badge-red active" id="btn-all" onclick="tcSetFilter('all')">All 30 Countries</div>
      <div class="tc-v4-badge tc-v4-badge-dark" id="btn-premium" onclick="tcSetFilter('premium')">120 Months (4)</div>
      <div class="tc-v4-badge tc-v4-badge-outline" id="btn-standard" onclick="tcSetFilter('standard')">3-Month (24)</div>
