    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 8px;">The Death of the Solo Business Visa</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;">Are you travelling to pitch a startup (B-1) or take a vacation (B-2)? To the US government, it doesn&#8217;t matter. Out of 522,721 total visas issued over the last three years across these 30 countries, pure business and tourism visas make up less than half a percent.</p>
    
