    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Search for any of the 30 tracked countries to see how their B-1/B-2 visa issuances rebounded after 2022.</p>
    
    <input type="text" id="tc-search-country" class="tc-v2-input" placeholder="Search for a country..." onkeyup="tcFilterList()">

