<div class="tc-v1-wrapper" id="tc-viz-1">
  <div class="tc-v1-box">
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 8px;">The Overstay Illusion (FY24)</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;">High percentages don&#8217;t always mean massive crowds. Toggle below to see how countries with the highest overstay rates often account for the fewest actual people.</p>
    
    <div class="tc-v1-btns">
